# Update App Icon Walkthrough

I have updated the app icon using the `flutter_launcher_icons` package.

## Changes
- **Icon Source**: Switched to [assets/images/new_app.png](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/assets/images/new_app.png) (moved from root [flutter_01.png](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/flutter_01.png) which was empty, found valid backup in assets).
- **Configuration**: Updated [pubspec.yaml](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/pubspec.yaml) to point to the new icon file.
- **Generation**: Ran `flutter pub run flutter_launcher_icons` to generate assets.

## Verification
### iOS
- Verified existence of icon files in `ios/Runner/Assets.xcassets/AppIcon.appiconset`.
- Files `Icon-App-*.png` are present with correct sizes.

### Android
- Verified existence of launcher icons in `android/app/src/main/res/`.
